<strong>Opoline Helm - AC 8</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/head.shtml">Head</a><BR>
Weight: 6.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/head.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/head.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/head.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/head.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/head.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in Oasis of Marr by Deepwater Goblins.<BR>

